title: Changes in Other Assets, Large Manufacturing Corporations for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1915-1922 (2)--Original Data, 1921-1943 "Other" Assets Include Investments: Positive Items Would Include Absorption Of Funds While Negative Items Would Include Release Of Funds. Source: Friedrich A. Lutz, Corporate Cash Balances 1914-1943, Manufacturing And Trade (1945), Pp.117-118, Columns 33 And 22.

This NBER data series a09056a appears on the NBER website in Chapter 9 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter09.html.
